## Dataset Licenses

This software does not bundle dataset data. Datasets are distributed as
separate OCI artifacts at ghcr.io/gillisandrew/linked-past/ and are pulled
at runtime. Each dataset has its own license:

| Dataset | License | SPDX |
|---------|---------|------|
| DPRR | CC BY-NC 4.0 | CC-BY-NC-4.0 |
| Pleiades | CC BY 3.0 | CC-BY-3.0 |
| PeriodO | CC0 1.0 | CC0-1.0 |
| Nomisma | CC BY 4.0 | CC-BY-4.0 |
| CRRO | ODbL 1.0 | ODbL-1.0 |
| EDH | CC BY-SA 4.0 | CC-BY-SA-4.0 |

License identifiers are declared in each OCI artifact's manifest annotations
(`org.opencontainers.image.licenses`). Consult the individual dataset's terms
before redistributing derived works.
